Schema Definitions

ENABLE:

Common node of traffic-engineering, policy, segment-list, candidate-paths, preference, path-info, metric, constraints, srte-interface, auto-route, on-demand-color

enable: null

True only

Example
{
  "enable": [ null ]
}

a1_sr_schema:

Segment Routing

enable: null

enable SR

mappings: object

Mapping Server

mapping: object[]

IP prefix to SID mapping

object
sid-range: integer

Range (number of SIDs)

flag-attached: string disable, enable

Enable/Disable Attached flag

af: string

Address Family

ip: string

IP prefix

mask: integer

Mask

sid-start: integer

Start of SID index range
